comments.body:
Hi [~vivi.xu], would you mind sharing file sizes of everything in {{work}} and {{cache}}? Please, paste results from:

{code}
find /var/lib/eucalyptus/instances/cache | xargs -L 1 ls -ld
find /var/lib/eucalyptus/instances/work | xargs -L 1 ls -ld
{code}

Also, I am curious how NC allocates the space that it has:

{code}
grep limit /var/log/eucalyptus/nc.log* | tail -6
{code}

Thanks!
